<h1 align="center">Yappi</h1>
<p align="center">
    Yet Another Python Profiler, but this time <b>thread&coroutine</b> aware.
</p>

<p align="center">
    <img src="https://www.travis-ci.org/sumerc/yappi.svg?branch=master">
